  "entries": [
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "D59538FBC28F664E6CE7550C0C222308E60549E0BF817BFAD22DE0CDD5ECD843",
      "id": 10959,
      "ko": "그렇다면 \u001bCA[bm1251]\u001bCZ이 진을 친 곳은 산 아래 \u001bCC하치만바라\u001bCZ…\n하지만 병력을 둘로 나누었다면\n\u001bCB다케다\u001bCZ의 본대는 빈틈이 많을 듯하옵니다.",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "EFB26E1265A9BED63A38D2C564DA7C9CEA7D7C15A5067D9D69EBBFF1326B9F6D",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "3239C77D1A4B5B735E137DDFC2F62A2A0E82B72AF85018826A2CFDF1CC71368C",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "3239C77D1A4B5B735E137DDFC2F62A2A0E82B72AF85018826A2CFDF1CC71368C"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "B0C9042F385B5DAB4B205ECB4D80D1C06FE7DF19F2A315510814F7D7D6B3663C",
      "id": 10960,
      "ko": "여기서는 \u001bCA[bm1251]\u001bCZ의 계책을 역이용해\n우리 일행은 이 산을 내려간다!\n결코 적에게 눈치채게 하지 마라!",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "104C66C0D5C8BE31FC768AFAF725E26DD9BA9C166DBE10670C30BABDB22D54CE",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "24D8CFCBA449FF9457A5FFD82F9D544FF0D35FDC74D471701616EEC0EED481AC",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "24D8CFCBA449FF9457A5FFD82F9D544FF0D35FDC74D471701616EEC0EED481AC"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "CA17B82116FCB5145A33E07E2F02999BFC39CF8905D7CEB5FE3E8A87236660A3",
      "id": 10962,
      "ko": "이국적인 풍모를 마음에 들어 한\n\u001bCA오다 노부나가\u001bCZ에게 직접 신변 경호의 임무를\n받고 있던 \u001bCA야스케\u001bCZ.",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "1F3B0ABC0446EE87C0FB19D95F384B8A514478A9F4D582D24E19CD3BB148FDBF",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "8B5E1C8AB100AA8E3057B628CA3123B984AE62DBC1CDA1AE6DF4AD9C84DE0AFE",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "8B5E1C8AB100AA8E3057B628CA3123B984AE62DBC1CDA1AE6DF4AD9C84DE0AFE"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "E77F07E100926F0E3D0963ED420A49577D2B9AE25BC1FA375F98FF079EE65A1F",
      "id": 10963,
      "ko": "주군이 된 \u001bCA노부나가\u001bCZ의 원정에 수행한 그는,\n\u001bCA노부나가\u001bCZ의 숙소인 \u001bCC교토\u001bCZ·\u001bCC혼노지\u001bCZ에서\n경내를 순찰하고 있었다…",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "2FA47C079630BECF1095DBFF36389D05B0BD4A6A42B90F25635E1244E16F8FF6",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "98EFA0E77BA9C8E24895CBFC5164FFF6D126F2F51D3209E078E2F59542E5BC8D",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "98EFA0E77BA9C8E24895CBFC5164FFF6D126F2F51D3209E078E2F59542E5BC8D"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "CF8CCFD736645578939575AB9C6C1DBFA55BDDC9401E69AF276AFE3B68C649C3",
      "id": 10964,
      "ko": "―덜컹!",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "0108245F9B78ED018A4DA3FD1BBA56028CD8BFC40BAA7E6A431D6AF04932DE13",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "C75DBAD5300C595180354F6D206F273D6D309904E63CE0FC324D9CDCB2A3C480",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "C75DBAD5300C595180354F6D206F273D6D309904E63CE0FC324D9CDCB2A3C480"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "2AC3DF9329B6AE80128857ED92442A0586A710CAA72820D9ABA917FB91C4C1E0",
      "id": 10965,
      "ko": "뭐야, 돌바닥이 어긋나 있지 않은가!\n…고쳐 두자. 다른 사람이\n걸려 넘어져도 곤란하겠지.",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "9D1E7A7F4FE102FA2369EF6CABBECAFE401CF2BEDD923BB686BEC0C0779E0708",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "09720BE55DE60EE544B1312B4B039F1091B01A251F67F4400752C7DB1F8F23F4",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "09720BE55DE60EE544B1312B4B039F1091B01A251F67F4400752C7DB1F8F23F4"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "B0C9042F385B5DAB4B205ECB4D80D1C06FE7DF19F2A315510814F7D7D6B3663C",
      "id": 10966,
      "ko": "돌바닥을 고치려던 \u001bCA야스케\u001bCZ가 판석을 들어내자\n그 판 모양 돌 뒤에는 깊은 굴이 있었다.\n굴은 꽤 깊어 지하로 이어지고 있다.",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "24EAE54DF7DCD847454EB44A42717C304967F7BD72385F7DFDA3AA0F4877B0DD",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "FC0B5F4C482E06CEBAFD5310E961B99761D202EE850E90B35EEC6062431C9C97",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "FC0B5F4C482E06CEBAFD5310E961B99761D202EE850E90B35EEC6062431C9C97"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "C16004F3EB0F55A42B855B8D584353FB303E73EEAA99957C517FB4989E65B8D3",
      "id": 10967,
      "ko": "이런 곳에 굴이 있다니…\n설마…숨은 길?",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "AF71F657BC110385480473D901D6993B8D4DBEFDB9BAB3DFCE11C87D0FC472E3",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "75083941EB725D28A499E5B5E855500C6305ACB08AF5E8A9AEEA73B9631373C5",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "75083941EB725D28A499E5B5E855500C6305ACB08AF5E8A9AEEA73B9631373C5"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "90C1DCD63135645CF8C17BAFE73CB3B872ACF1B637372D4A767AE42721AF6FB5",
      "id": 10968,
      "ko": "―\u001bCA야스케\u001bCZ 님! 여기 계셨습니까!\n주군께서 부르십니다, 서둘러 본당으로!",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "0B4A6491CEF956EDBB5DDEF5C882BDA82A188B37F6BEE9ABE8E7E2B08E122892",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "42D3F69041D5358B9C5CA9467191A4B61A6EE6108B9A140A76532D57F26FFB52",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "42D3F69041D5358B9C5CA9467191A4B61A6EE6108B9A140A76532D57F26FFB52"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "C16004F3EB0F55A42B855B8D584353FB303E73EEAA99957C517FB4989E65B8D3",
      "id": 10969,
      "ko": "뭐라고!\n즉시 가겠소!",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "3DE304A4FD7BDBF9373720B173A08C266D18B5253E5BF81DD64E7B0A56BA9C3E",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "294C564661E44E9F06FDDB902471F7EE6342129D113C6574A7A275919D73BB7D",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "294C564661E44E9F06FDDB902471F7EE6342129D113C6574A7A275919D73BB7D"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "2AC3DF9329B6AE80128857ED92442A0586A710CAA72820D9ABA917FB91C4C1E0",
      "id": 10970,
      "ko": "（절에 숨겨진 굴이라니,\n　정체가 궁금하지만…\n　이 입구는 닫아 두도록 하자）",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "91ABB02E8AADF6AAF8923ACD04A40412DA46DE78CD41EF5123E94B77B4C1CE8A",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "BCFCA4C1C45FC5CF59EB84409AF1FBAD38D3258026B17A30E773D7DF25ADED33",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "BCFCA4C1C45FC5CF59EB84409AF1FBAD38D3258026B17A30E773D7DF25ADED33"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "3F42839EFEABEF40C9A8364BA0943ECF51BE0FBF4F6210D9A1E7F08AC02BFE2F",
      "id": 10971,
      "ko": "이튿날, 새벽의 \u001bCC혼노지\u001bCZ 문 앞―",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "68ACE27BB024086D70744C439290245B4C5CAD89C135786CE68340D0A215EB15",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "4A747B955C8EEB8EB7CE66A830A2C14E3FAB5F7D5CD299E11378F934A1AE9051",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "4A747B955C8EEB8EB7CE66A830A2C14E3FAB5F7D5CD299E11378F934A1AE9051"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "C16004F3EB0F55A42B855B8D584353FB303E73EEAA99957C517FB4989E65B8D3",
      "id": 10972,
      "ko": "새가 지저귀기 시작했군…\n야번도 슬슬 끝날 때가 되었나.",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "F8550CB182AD4321595CB4C1048EE4D065C9AAAF3D7DCD62AF3586BEB9EFFD05",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "CA95463BD0E8F1FBA668340C5CCC4F7628EDC6BFE5D4867DB30672EA84561860",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "CA95463BD0E8F1FBA668340C5CCC4F7628EDC6BFE5D4867DB30672EA84561860"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "2AC3DF9329B6AE80128857ED92442A0586A710CAA72820D9ABA917FB91C4C1E0",
      "id": 10973,
      "ko": "（그러고 보니,\n　그 숨은 길은 어디로 이어져 있었을까…\n　보물창고인가, 아니면 밖으로 빠져나가는 길인가）",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "A80CEC5E1F6CE4A5CB21F51319D0398A0C523E47A04C732658E03F8C1EE625FA",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "C52C067903F6E93E7526DA48D152A3BDC467F986501C9F860E3D550B98EDBE6A",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "C52C067903F6E93E7526DA48D152A3BDC467F986501C9F860E3D550B98EDBE6A"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "B0C9042F385B5DAB4B205ECB4D80D1C06FE7DF19F2A315510814F7D7D6B3663C",
      "id": 10974,
      "ko": "불침번 근무가 끝날 무렵,\n생각에 잠긴 \u001bCA야스케\u001bCZ의 귀에 들려온 것은\n규칙적으로 행군하는 부대의 발소리였다.",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "AAB94AC11EE898B8D5599AEAEA9CBD03A4C8418EB1C25077FDD4D83238084E3A",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "C34DA58C60A173134139823A00CDA1B63558FD5CC8C04D1A2501B5D37014FDCD",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "C34DA58C60A173134139823A00CDA1B63558FD5CC8C04D1A2501B5D37014FDCD"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "CA33098B2D87F14221E3BFD5271B16FFF4ADB4FE97CA10FC1B523B5BB8EF0C36",
      "id": 10975,
      "ko": "병력이 \u001bCC교토\u001bCZ를 지날 예정은 없었는데…\n…설마 누군가의 배신인가!?\n한시라도 빨리 알려야 한다!",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "4877062E570D279D8FA8340AD38843E050E24B30A8202580BD1CD55786F6FC37",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "3348F206AB334960385185136DD4450659306B728FE1951CDA7E69864BA4C220",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "3348F206AB334960385185136DD4450659306B728FE1951CDA7E69864BA4C220"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "2E8CC62AAF4B4FCA747B5FC7EC970521707416ABB7A01EC950D1E1AB71371ACC",
      "id": 10976,
      "ko": "\u001bCC혼노지\u001bCZ, \u001bCA오다 노부나가\u001bCZ의 침소―",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "5795E05D35ED523D330637CCD7F9313A0D818DABF00497222858D38DCE76FB67",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "AF5AF52D94128F6287504D6A3860DEA22595E90B34CDF3BAF9684103D8EDF0E4",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "AF5AF52D94128F6287504D6A3860DEA22595E90B34CDF3BAF9684103D8EDF0E4"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "CA17B82116FCB5145A33E07E2F02999BFC39CF8905D7CEB5FE3E8A87236660A3",
      "id": 10977,
      "ko": "\u001bCA야스케\u001bCZ가 침소로 달려 들어갔을 때는 이미,\n마찬가지로 반란을 눈치챈 이들이\n\u001bCA노부나가\u001bCZ 곁에 모여 있었다.",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "3FD9AECF11DFA45FC4243A7CA0EB94FAC100717537118F998A1B55620E7ABC45",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "5814D8CF56B726E8F8B4030157447BFCAA4C186AD1CBCFD4C90EBC959EA90B66",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "5814D8CF56B726E8F8B4030157447BFCAA4C186AD1CBCFD4C90EBC959EA90B66"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "CA17B82116FCB5145A33E07E2F02999BFC39CF8905D7CEB5FE3E8A87236660A3",
      "id": 10978,
      "ko": "오오, \u001bCA야스케\u001bCZ! 너도 들었느냐?\n쳐들어온 군의 깃발은 도라지 문양이야…\n…설마 \u001bCA미쓰히데\u001bCZ가 반란을 일으킬 줄이야, 방심했군!",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "C6B1625E4E139C00209D5FBB0B94D69A32726E3EAFB68758664866485436B8CB",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "B132947BC0269F430890CC9CC3603BBA97DACAA79A8D01132E6DF293EFDD8FB4",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "B132947BC0269F430890CC9CC3603BBA97DACAA79A8D01132E6DF293EFDD8FB4"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "CA33098B2D87F14221E3BFD5271B16FFF4ADB4FE97CA10FC1B523B5BB8EF0C36",
      "id": 10979,
      "ko": "이렇게 된 이상 어쩔 수 없습니다.\n무슨 수를 써서라도 포위를 뚫고\n\u001bCC오미\u001bCZ 방면으로 빠져나가야 합니다…",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "73880FA9360F2F27249557DA7C7391A8FA8036A5249B10ADF449073E75C2EBF6",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "2A1D1619CBCF8BDD55E354992B9837FBC4913CBB7F63DC26A9DC418979284CE1",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "2A1D1619CBCF8BDD55E354992B9837FBC4913CBB7F63DC26A9DC418979284CE1"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "6C8B16D368A0A938F36CC451A6E9B41031DCA38A3C22C7F79D3A72D022CB6AA4",
      "id": 10980,
      "ko": "\u001bCC니조\u001bCZ 방면은 포위가 두터울 것입니다.\n돌파한다면 남문이―",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "5962FE92193BB2E9412F779CD121C3275B110BB9CD38B85BB2AF5A2C14247A6F",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "B34DED9B4802BA6CD2233CA18D2D67BE65EABCFD27AB46AD5E24502DBA8E33D2",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "B34DED9B4802BA6CD2233CA18D2D67BE65EABCFD27AB46AD5E24502DBA8E33D2"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "90C1DCD63135645CF8C17BAFE73CB3B872ACF1B637372D4A767AE42721AF6FB5",
      "id": 10981,
      "ko": "착착 군의가 진행되는 가운데,\n\u001bCA야스케\u001bCZ는 홀로 망설이고 있었다.",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "58580FAAFDE9AFDA8E2E1363BC11D595F2579B80963F13F46EB00C7B95D2E9C4",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "6D3B2913D8FB9A3110E9E454D2DD8E1B2A5922807F8AAB95E0FD7B1680CBA620",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "6D3B2913D8FB9A3110E9E454D2DD8E1B2A5922807F8AAB95E0FD7B1680CBA620"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "C16004F3EB0F55A42B855B8D584353FB303E73EEAA99957C517FB4989E65B8D3",
      "id": 10982,
      "ko": "（그 숨은 길의 존재를\n　주군과 모두에게 알려야 할까）",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "78EC339E08694F0D868AF0A7544828C6F5C2A83567468D78123C7E986E38EB6E",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "1F290CE6DCD08F43881F4ABCC65F0E3C0008EFB941E8CB141E6C2DFCE047B043",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "1F290CE6DCD08F43881F4ABCC65F0E3C0008EFB941E8CB141E6C2DFCE047B043"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "CA17B82116FCB5145A33E07E2F02999BFC39CF8905D7CEB5FE3E8A87236660A3",
      "id": 10983,
      "ko": "（\u001bCA미쓰히데\u001bCZ 님의 주도면밀함은 주군께서 가장 잘 아신다…\n　주군께서는 \u001bCA아케치\u001bCZ군의 포위를 돌파하는 것보다\n　숨은 길로 탈출하는 길을 택하실 것이다. 하지만）",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "287C14130DA59A6BA658708B7E60786478B89811236FD26A0FF913F44DFFBF52",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "DFAE840906A1AD5D10E9C40AA43A71B3409B4CA5221B440B90F2115D30BBDF29",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "DFAE840906A1AD5D10E9C40AA43A71B3409B4CA5221B440B90F2115D30BBDF29"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "2AC3DF9329B6AE80128857ED92442A0586A710CAA72820D9ABA917FB91C4C1E0",
      "id": 10984,
      "ko": "（그 길이 밖으로 이어진다는 증거는 없다.\n　만약 막다른 길이라면, 이 선택은\n　모두의 죽음을 확실하게 만들고 만다）",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "333B45EECE963879341175098F9982784BD0362F659D50F48CB3B3C2B1F4DC42",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "73C595CC33CEBCB1C4DF412ED0298355445D4371B3B83300C4C70E07149B760F",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "73C595CC33CEBCB1C4DF412ED0298355445D4371B3B83300C4C70E07149B760F"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "C16004F3EB0F55A42B855B8D584353FB303E73EEAA99957C517FB4989E65B8D3",
      "id": 10985,
      "ko": "（완전한 도박이 된다.\n　나는―）",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "06021C9DDB8E4348ED8840A189E6200DABDED6BF37653B727533B2037D6987F7",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "D1FC3313D6AEA7518111009EF57AA68AB89AF090FDEF06F109DD8B727B406A04",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "D1FC3313D6AEA7518111009EF57AA68AB89AF090FDEF06F109DD8B727B406A04"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "2AC3DF9329B6AE80128857ED92442A0586A710CAA72820D9ABA917FB91C4C1E0",
      "id": 10986,
      "ko": "（정체를 알 수 없는 숨은 길에\n　모두의 목숨을 걸 수는 없다.\n　전투 준비에 집중하자）",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "D85891BDEF1982406B7EAFCA455AE5CBAF4A01D94F906D49D3CE00C8CFF298A5",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "21F346AA920336FE76FA5AFA742F9C29E866F817CC3B2E399776EAC65118BB10",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "21F346AA920336FE76FA5AFA742F9C29E866F817CC3B2E399776EAC65118BB10"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "CA17B82116FCB5145A33E07E2F02999BFC39CF8905D7CEB5FE3E8A87236660A3",
      "id": 10987,
      "ko": "작전은 정리되었다!\n\u001bCA아케치\u001bCZ군의 포위만 뚫으면 우리가 이긴다…\n\u001bCA야스케\u001bCZ, 함께 가자!",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "3584B846083E00DD9B1AA99B26EE36513CDEE592773550E5242F5EA170D3A6D5",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "539E485F99B49924902F292EEA269C5C6D66E7FD4CA74B5A39C01F765FDCE8B5",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "539E485F99B49924902F292EEA269C5C6D66E7FD4CA74B5A39C01F765FDCE8B5"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "CA17B82116FCB5145A33E07E2F02999BFC39CF8905D7CEB5FE3E8A87236660A3",
      "id": 10988,
      "ko": "\u001bCA노부나가\u001bCZ를 따라 밖으로 나온 \u001bCA야스케\u001bCZ의 귀에\n조금 전보다 커진 행군 소리가 들려온다.\n사투의 때가 바로 눈앞까지 다가왔다…",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "2D84335703CC277973E600B0EC593883EA04E7D9AAAE8A57BC34F01542D88C88",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "19FF4D97D6D7BFE459ACE15AECDBD94FF36DFFD1520A57C5F979D9C022EA3478",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "19FF4D97D6D7BFE459ACE15AECDBD94FF36DFFD1520A57C5F979D9C022EA3478"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "C16004F3EB0F55A42B855B8D584353FB303E73EEAA99957C517FB4989E65B8D3",
      "id": 10989,
      "ko": "（운을 하늘에 맡길 뿐이다.\n　여기서는 도박을 해 보는 수밖에 없다）",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "030345A9393FD33150DDF94699298CBC913B67EAC92136CCE63005731FDFF7B7",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "89E0FFA977C075AE20892A3AAB4E12B9FAC855B8C725D5ADF31091C9B6E95C84",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "89E0FFA977C075AE20892A3AAB4E12B9FAC855B8C725D5ADF31091C9B6E95C84"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "CA33098B2D87F14221E3BFD5271B16FFF4ADB4FE97CA10FC1B523B5BB8EF0C36",
      "id": 10990,
      "ko": "주군, 들어 주십시오!\n이 \u001bCC혼노지\u001bCZ 지하에는 숨은 길이 있습니다…\n운이 좋으면 밖으로 빠져나갈 수도 있을지 모릅니다.",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "4D4E28BD9E99B40CF7DC08BCEDDC7825A667ADF3D0078677DCA9845A91782F3C",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "155E6641F1A2EFE33A861A27FD99C8A92CAB241A9A4B55DFA21542F4C0DFC694",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "155E6641F1A2EFE33A861A27FD99C8A92CAB241A9A4B55DFA21542F4C0DFC694"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "C16004F3EB0F55A42B855B8D584353FB303E73EEAA99957C517FB4989E65B8D3",
      "id": 10991,
      "ko": "뭐라고…?\n운, 운인가…",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "D447A002C5FDF74F18CBB5B88CCB370149BD42DD287E9C4D210C8C58E2C1D8CE",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "4B7E8F771D8FE0AFE509242832CB8091ABE4151D0CF47B5A079342F7BF305CC2",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "4B7E8F771D8FE0AFE509242832CB8091ABE4151D0CF47B5A079342F7BF305CC2"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "2AC3DF9329B6AE80128857ED92442A0586A710CAA72820D9ABA917FB91C4C1E0",
      "id": 10992,
      "ko": "…좋다!\n네 운에 모든 것을 맡긴다!\n당장 안내하라!",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "946E44874E2FEEB89468796EEE0278B25AD851D4616F13C4C5344828FA5BE7ED",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "48EBB7D0E6DABD014FE09F480C803B9FA3F16E477118F506F5ED56DBE5B5BD5E",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "48EBB7D0E6DABD014FE09F480C803B9FA3F16E477118F506F5ED56DBE5B5BD5E"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "3F42839EFEABEF40C9A8364BA0943ECF51BE0FBF4F6210D9A1E7F08AC02BFE2F",
      "id": 10993,
      "ko": "\u001bCC혼노지\u001bCZ, 지하―",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "FC0CD4325A240757FFBA00473CFFC16A66CB699D6571E4AD4A70F6C8764A2E76",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "DD637B8AE4A5FC57649BDD01C0F5691BC5BD62F2DC0AA56FAEDA3BFEFC0A0748",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "DD637B8AE4A5FC57649BDD01C0F5691BC5BD62F2DC0AA56FAEDA3BFEFC0A0748"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "C16004F3EB0F55A42B855B8D584353FB303E73EEAA99957C517FB4989E65B8D3",
      "id": 10994,
      "ko": "설마 절 지하에\n이렇게 긴 길이 있을 줄이야…",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "F23ED9F7EE0AA22221071F5BBBA78CED467BEAD4492F5DECF23C1EDB32259DE6",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "2B9E045D6074EC3638189E487065F68832A7318B40B7FC604D875ACE4FFE6868",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "2B9E045D6074EC3638189E487065F68832A7318B40B7FC604D875ACE4FFE6868"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "CA33098B2D87F14221E3BFD5271B16FFF4ADB4FE97CA10FC1B523B5BB8EF0C36",
      "id": 10995,
      "ko": "그러게 말입니다…\n전란이 끊이지 않는 \u001bCC교토\u001bCZ의 거리이기에\n만일의 탈출구를 마련해 둔 것이겠지요만…",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "BC392C267AE002B8E384462EAE6B5998036199BE5F8E6A6EA128FEDA8C8BC07A",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "D8B70A79E01B7E6E6E1BB9F3751EC1B2DA3E60DD79C5D389DF7B3A57F0E13E68",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "D8B70A79E01B7E6E6E1BB9F3751EC1B2DA3E60DD79C5D389DF7B3A57F0E13E68"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "2AC3DF9329B6AE80128857ED92442A0586A710CAA72820D9ABA917FB91C4C1E0",
      "id": 10996,
      "ko": "다행히 숨은 길은 막다른 곳에 이르지 않고,\n구불구불하며 앞으로 이어지고 있었다.\n그리고…",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "509248F7B3395158F3FDD70F7222F3277A3167D7E3553C110CCADAF9ACCD2AB8",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "91506E4DEA1D660E3C3AEBA9938E70BBD7E0D2BA52BF60B83CC859D5CFA2A8B5",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "91506E4DEA1D660E3C3AEBA9938E70BBD7E0D2BA52BF60B83CC859D5CFA2A8B5"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "C16004F3EB0F55A42B855B8D584353FB303E73EEAA99957C517FB4989E65B8D3",
      "id": 10997,
      "ko": "주군, 여러분!\n이 굽이를 지나면 빛이 보입니다!",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "F5BA0E99C48A60B3A406569D329489BE6BE13D5945024FAC7B01744CA16A2272",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "62ACE6729120AB985FEDDD11AAA4F01DFFA94A3DCB39DBF702F81BCD31B3FF9E",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "62ACE6729120AB985FEDDD11AAA4F01DFFA94A3DCB39DBF702F81BCD31B3FF9E"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "B0C9042F385B5DAB4B205ECB4D80D1C06FE7DF19F2A315510814F7D7D6B3663C",
      "id": 10998,
      "ko": "하하, 정말 포위 밖으로 나올 수 있었다니!\n이제 일단 죽을 고비는 벗어난 듯하구나…\n\u001bCA야스케\u001bCZ, 잘했다!",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "5D018DCFDAFEF35AC92040FF181BD2882042259D1255B5800BB60F1A4CAA4D78",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "0F99E2AF94057708D6CC57EBAD3AB5F64A9B368429AB70761F921D1C084660F4",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "0F99E2AF94057708D6CC57EBAD3AB5F64A9B368429AB70761F921D1C084660F4"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "BF5FAC6CE47563D1B9E8F7660FC61EB91E713B4E0A546C327045851804586443",
      "id": 10999,
      "ko": "\u001bCA야스케\u001bCZ의 기지로 살아남은 \u001bCA노부나가\u001bCZ 일행.\n그들은 반역자 \u001bCA아케치 미쓰히데\u001bCZ에 맞서기 위해,\n\u001bCC교토\u001bCZ를 벗어나 본거지·\u001bCC아즈치성\u001bCZ으로 향했다…",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "BF2D4972E67606B6823D2469511C7A14F7E870B84AA0DAB88C34973FEEF1E2B2",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "3A958504CBC04BE3C32C09E2C3657F6E2EB2674D0D4622DA638F96CD79E1F577",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "3A958504CBC04BE3C32C09E2C3657F6E2EB2674D0D4622DA638F96CD79E1F577"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "B18DC220A16356A0CEE1F9BA0027796B79CBB01B51F115E17B87176505E1E4E3",
      "id": 11000,
      "ko": "\u001bCA아케치 미쓰히데\u001bCZ의 배신으로부터 며칠 뒤, \u001bCC아즈치성\u001bCZ―",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "6D9038E624779BF15FDD338F77332998147EF5E653B6462457BC09769144D9B8",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "A3E01C1A71D56C4F0773249FA291055772B54EA0B070CADB0CA8CA2F5CA773A8",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "A3E01C1A71D56C4F0773249FA291055772B54EA0B070CADB0CA8CA2F5CA773A8"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "CF8CCFD736645578939575AB9C6C1DBFA55BDDC9401E69AF276AFE3B68C649C3",
      "id": 11001,
      "ko": "주군! 무사히 여기까지 돌아오시다니!",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "F6BFE4584D0DA7A5016507710E0602D45871DB8B50C9E567C552BFDACF5473AE",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "839800EA367560CFF3DA9D160B9F9F2323450BC887322348CB304C95E754470B",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "839800EA367560CFF3DA9D160B9F9F2323450BC887322348CB304C95E754470B"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "B0C9042F385B5DAB4B205ECB4D80D1C06FE7DF19F2A315510814F7D7D6B3663C",
      "id": 11002,
      "ko": "하하, 마침내 하늘에게 버림받았다고 생각했지만,\n\u001bCA야스케\u001bCZ의 기지 덕을 봤다!\n…그래서, 정세는?",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "D9218E0C380F4D5903E6C4D84E06D3B8D41A53EFBDDBF8DE5E2DA4CE4C23730F",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "D825C842E2F283859A4EE2357CBBE731D53B3E3192190AB5E63E9FB7E05E9C61",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "D825C842E2F283859A4EE2357CBBE731D53B3E3192190AB5E63E9FB7E05E9C61"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "CA17B82116FCB5145A33E07E2F02999BFC39CF8905D7CEB5FE3E8A87236660A3",
      "id": 11003,
      "ko": "\u001bCA아케치\u001bCZ 님의 반란에서 며칠이 지나,\n\u001bCA오다 노부나가\u001bCZ가 죽었다는 풍문이\n영지 전역을 뒤덮고 있습니다.",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "B287EB1BA090A7DB31010AC3B68ECFA6518C744C9C4DF9CDB118AAAF73D22E92",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "D0E70372AC44119B6E311A5D579830744D1B1F37572B256A954C769201628700",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "D0E70372AC44119B6E311A5D579830744D1B1F37572B256A954C769201628700"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "CA17B82116FCB5145A33E07E2F02999BFC39CF8905D7CEB5FE3E8A87236660A3",
      "id": 11004,
      "ko": "\u001bCA하시바\u001bCZ 님, \u001bCA시바타\u001bCZ 님 같은 중신 여러분도\n주군을 찾기보다는 다음 천하를\n차지하려는 듯한 분위기라서…",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "8086EB320E64776719059DC374836E6054CF9C3DE41E4AEDA1E3CF403BCACDEE",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "23622C4E81AF57914CD1E6AF454B41300656540F1365C72D6C1354D698CCFF8F",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "23622C4E81AF57914CD1E6AF454B41300656540F1365C72D6C1354D698CCFF8F"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "B0C9042F385B5DAB4B205ECB4D80D1C06FE7DF19F2A315510814F7D7D6B3663C",
      "id": 11005,
      "ko": "됐다…\n그 \u001bCA미쓰히데\u001bCZ마저 배신했다.\n중신 따위 누구도 믿을 수 없다!",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "E7ECCCE897B84AC62B80ACD158723E5768214FFDCA3FB85787F4D0B37AB21D7D",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "C92D6721014ADEBEDB1979B3DA8C93F8D5C6F62895661071085A866D31CA4602",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "C92D6721014ADEBEDB1979B3DA8C93F8D5C6F62895661071085A866D31CA4602"
    },
    {
      "category": "event_story_residual",
      "format_invariants_sha256": "EA10805C3885474DC2BD053B682E0E9506A90E3FF0B92EC211BE98D517506BAD",
      "id": 11006,
      "ko": "이제 이 땅은 사방 모두가 적이다!\n…\u001bCA야스케\u001bCZ, \u001bCA란마루\u001bCZ, \u001bCA야스히데\u001bCZ!\n여기서 다시 천하를 차지해 보이겠다!",
      "ko_utf16le_sha256": "5C0AF5D03A964D1040E074E5769E77045840F66BF7BCE28C0EA7D2D78BE0D1FF",
      "source_jp_utf16le_sha256": "6DBED3221C8F5524DC44B350EA1FCD74C32B293C5EFEEA01C4B1A6513666ED7D",
      "wave08_baseline_utf16le_sha256": "6DBED3221C8F5524DC44B350EA1FCD74C32B293C5EFEEA01C4B1A6513666ED7D"
    },
